title: Carmageddon + Splat Pack Windows LAN TCP/IP [ENG/FULL]
description:
Windows Version of Carmageddon and Splat Pack, Works Fine on New OS'es without IPX/SPX protocol.

This Release Contains Movies and Audio and High Resolution Run Mode.

On All GFX Cards Please Set Vsync=on

System Requirements: Windows 95+, Pentium 1 100 Mhz 16MB Ram

Proof Video: Playing Carmageddon on 3 PC's (1 WiFi + 2 LAN in Windows XP, Windows 2000, Windows XP x64)
